###############################################################################
This is the readme for the program to get "Rotten Tomatoes" ratings for any movie
##############################################################################
1.clone the git repository & run docker.sh file as follows.

# chmod 777 docker.sh
# sh docker.sh

Now you will be inside your docker container.
Note: docker should be installed in your server.

2. How to run script.

- Go to the required directory i.e. movie_rating_api_code
# cd /movie_rating_api_code

-Run following command:
# python rating.py <Title of Movie>

eg; python rating.py "dark phoenix"
or python rating.py "Bharat" 

